---
import '../styles/steps.css';
import coverFire from '../assets/cover-fire.jpeg';
---

<div class="vrail" aria-hidden="true"><span class="rd"></span><span class="rd"></span><span class="rd"></span><span
    class="rd"></span></div>

<main class="how" id="how">
  <div class="how-intro">
    <span class="step-k">Así se crea un plan</span>
    <h2>De la idea al plan, <em>en minutos.</em></h2>
  </div>

  <!-- ════ 01 · ENTRAR ════ -->
  <section class="step" data-screen-label="Flujo · Entrar">
    <div class="copy">
      <span class="step-k">01 · Entra</span>
      <h2><em>Ingresa en</em> segundos </h2>
      <ul class="ticks">
        <li>Entra con tu correo</li>
        <li>Sin contraseñas que recordar</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="device">
      <div class="phone">
        <div class="scr" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="sbar"><span>10:42</span><span class="sbar-ic"><i></i><i></i><i></i><b></b></span></div>
          <div class="abody">
            <b class="atitle">Únete al plan</b>
            <span class="asub">Solo para avisarte de tus planes. Cero spam 🙂</span>
            <span class="afield">tucorreo@gmail.com<span class="acaret"></span></span>
            <span class="abtn">Enviar código</span>
            <span class="adiv">o entra con</span>
            <div class="asso">
              <span class="sso"><span class="mk">G</span>Google</span>
              <span class="sso"><span class="mk wa">✆</span>WhatsApp</span>
              <span class="sso"><span class="mk fb">f</span>Facebook</span>
            </div>
            <div class="aperks">
              <span>Foto de perfil opcional</span>
              <span>Sin pedir tu cumpleaños</span>
              <span>Sin contraseñas</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════ 02 · CREAR Y PERSONALIZAR ════ -->
  <section class="step" data-screen-label="Flujo · Crear">
    <div class="copy">
      <span class="step-k">02 · Crea</span>
      <h2>Tu plan, <em>a tu estilo.</em></h2>
      <ul class="ticks">
        <li>Crealo en menos de un minuto</li>
        <li>Portadas y estilos para cada ocasión</li>
        <li>Cambia lo que quieras después - todos se enteran solos</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="device">
      <div class="phone">
        <div class="scr" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="sbar"><span>10:42</span><span class="sbar-ic"><i></i><i></i><i></i><b></b></span></div>
          <div class="chead"><b>Nuevo plan</b><span class="cx">✕</span></div>
          <div class="covprev covphoto" style={`background-image:url(${coverFire.src})`}><span class="covtag">PORTADA</span></div>
          <div class="covpick">
            <span class="sw gx-fire on"></span>
            <span class="sw gx-cake"></span>
            <span class="sw gx-trip"></span>
            <span class="sw gx-fest"></span>
            <span class="sw gx-grad"></span>
            <span class="swlbl">Estilo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cfield focus">
            <small>Nombre del plan</small>
            <b>Parrillada en lo de Fer<span class="acaret"></span></b>
          </div>
          <div class="cgrid">
            <div class="cfield"><small>Cuándo</small><b>📅 Sáb · 8 PM</b></div>
            <div class="cfield"><small>Dónde</small><b>📍 Mi casa</b></div>
          </div>
          <div class="cfield">
            <small>Lista de cosas</small>
            <b>🍻 Chelas · 🧊 Pisco · 🍗 Chorizo</b>
          </div>
          <div class="cbtn">Crear plan ✦</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════ 03 · COMPARTIR ════ -->
  <section class="step" data-screen-label="Flujo · Compartir">
    <div class="copy">
      <span class="step-k">03 · Comparte</span>
      <h2>Un link <em> y estamos yendi</em></h2>
      <ul class="ticks">
        <li>Compartelo donde quieras</li>
        <li>Confirman sin descargar nada</li>
        <li>Todos coordinados en un solo lugar</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="device">
      <div class="phone">
        <div class="scr" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="sbar"><span>10:43</span><span class="sbar-ic"><i></i><i></i><i></i><b></b></span></div>
          <div class="shero">
            <span class="big">🎉</span>
            <b>¡Plan creado!</b>
            <small>Ahora invítalos — esto se arma solo</small>
          </div>
          <div class="slink">yendi.app/p/parrillada-fer<span class="scopy">Copiar</span></div>
          <div class="swa">✆ Compartir por WhatsApp</div>
          <div class="sdiv">o invita directo</div>
          <div class="frow"><span class="av c2">J</span><span class="fmeta"><b>Joro</b><small>Siempre se
                apunta</small></span><span class="finv ok">Invitado ✓</span></div>
          <div class="frow"><span class="av c4">C</span><span class="fmeta"><b>Caro</b><small>Fue a tu última
                parrillada</small></span><span class="finv ok">Invitado ✓</span></div>
          <div class="frow"><span class="av c3">D</span><span class="fmeta"><b>Diego</b><small>De tu grupo del
                barrio</small></span><span class="finv todo">Invitar</span></div>
          <div class="frow"><span class="av c5">P</span><span class="fmeta"><b>Pau</b><small>De tu grupo del
                barrio</small></span><span class="finv todo">Invitar</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════ 04 · RSVP ════ -->
  <section class="step" data-screen-label="Flujo · RSVP">
    <div class="copy">
      <span class="step-k">04 · Confirmaciones</span>
      <h2>Mira quién va, <em>en vivo.</em></h2>
      <p>Tus amigos responden con un toque y tú ves todo al instante: quiénes van, quién lleva qué y qué falta.</p>
      <ul class="ticks">
        <li>Yendi · Tal vez · No — un toque y listo</li>
        <li>Cada quien agarra algo de la lista</li>
        <li>Cero “¿al final quiénes van?” en el chat</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="device">
      <div class="phone">
        <div class="scr" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="sbar"><span>10:51</span><span class="sbar-ic"><i></i><i></i><i></i><b></b></span></div>
          <div class="ecover covphoto" style={`height:104px;background-image:url(${coverFire.src})`}><span class="when">SÁB · 8
              PM</span></div>
          <div class="ehead">
            <b class="etitle">Parrillada en lo de Fer</b>
            <span class="ehost">Te invitó Nico · 📍 Su casa</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rseg">
            <span class="ropt on">Yendi ✓</span>
            <span class="ropt">Tal vez</span>
            <span class="ropt">No</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rcount">
            <span class="avrow"><span class="av c1">N</span><span class="av c2">J</span><span
                class="av c4">C</span><span class="av c3">D</span><span class="avmore">+8</span></span>
            <small>12 van · 3 tal vez</small>
          </div>
          <div class="brhead">¿Quién lleva qué?</div>
          <div class="brow"><span class="bk done">✓</span>Chelas<span class="who">Joro</span></div>
          <div class="brow mine"><span class="bk done">✓</span>Pisco<span class="who">Tú 🙌</span></div>
          <div class="brow"><span class="bk open">✓</span>Chorizo<span class="who">Libre</span></div>
          <div class="toast"><span class="av c1">N</span>Nico: “¡Buenaza! Nos vemos el sábado 🎉”</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<style>
  /* ---- section shell ---- */
  .how {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8, 6, 5, 0), rgba(8, 6, 5, .66) 180px, rgba(8, 6, 5, .84));
    padding: 90px 0 30px;
  }

  .how-intro {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 10px;
    padding: 0 26px;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .how-intro h2,
  .copy h2 {
    font-family: "Clash Display", "Hanken Grotesk", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -.015em;
    line-height: 1.07;
    text-wrap: balance;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 18%, #ecdfc8 92%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .how-intro h2 {
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4.6vw, 40px);
  }

  .copy h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4.6vw, 42px);
  }

  .how-intro h2 em,
  .copy h2 em {
    font-family: "Cormorant", "Clash Display", Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.12em;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    color: var(--lux);
    -webkit-text-fill-color: var(--lux);
    padding-right: .06em;
  }

  /* alternate row direction for even steps */
  .step:nth-of-type(even) {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  /* ---- copy column ---- */
  .copy {
    flex: 1 1 300px;
    max-width: 430px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .copy p {
    font-size: 15.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 42ch;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .ticks {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 11px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .ticks li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 11px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 450;
    color: rgba(241, 232, 219, .85);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ticks li::before {
    content: "✦";
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--lux);
    translate: 0 -1px;
  }

  /* ---- mobile progress rail ---- */
  .vrail {
    position: fixed;
    top: max(16px, env(safe-area-inset-top));
    left: 50%;
    translate: -50% 0;
    z-index: 40;
    display: none;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .vrail .rd {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(232, 207, 160, .3);
    transition: all .45s cubic-bezier(.4, 0, .2, 1);
  }

  .vrail .rd.on {
    width: 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--lux);
  }

  /* ---- device: metallic phone frame with champagne rim ---- */
  .device {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .device::before {
    /* ambient champagne glow behind the phone */
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    z-index: -1;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    translate: -50% -50%;
    width: 430px;
    height: 430px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232, 207, 160, .13), rgba(232, 207, 160, .04) 42%, transparent 64%);
  }

  .device::after {
    /* contact shadow on the floor */
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    z-index: -1;
    left: 50%;
    bottom: -30px;
    translate: -50% 0;
    width: 230px;
    height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(50% 50% at 50% 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, .6), transparent 72%);
    filter: blur(5px);
  }

  .phone {
    width: 294px;
    height: 618px;
    border-radius: 44px;
    padding: 10px;
    position: relative;
    border: none;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #332b23, #100d0b 36%, #1c1714 68%, #3b3128);
    box-shadow:
      0 70px 120px -28px rgba(0, 0, 0, .72),
      0 28px 50px -16px rgba(0, 0, 0, .55),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(243, 227, 194, .18);
  }

  .phone::before {
    /* island */
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 19px;
    left: 50%;
    translate: -50% 0;
    width: 78px;
    height: 21px;
    border-radius: 11px;
    background: #000;
    z-index: 6;
  }

  .phone::after {
    /* champagne metal rim */
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 44px;
    padding: 1.2px;
    z-index: 7;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, rgba(232, 207, 160, .65), rgba(255, 255, 255, .14) 28%, rgba(255, 255, 255, .03) 48%, rgba(232, 207, 160, .12) 70%, rgba(232, 207, 160, .45));
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    mask: linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
    mask-composite: exclude;
  }

  /* ---- phone screen + status bar ---- */
  .scr {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 36px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    background: #0c0a09;
    color: #f2ece6;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-family: "General Sans", system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  .sbar {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 15px 24px 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .85);
  }

  .sbar-ic {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 2.5px;
  }

  .sbar-ic i {
    width: 3px;
    border-radius: 1px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .8);
  }

  .sbar-ic i:nth-child(1) { height: 4px; }
  .sbar-ic i:nth-child(2) { height: 6px; }
  .sbar-ic i:nth-child(3) { height: 8px; }

  .sbar-ic b {
    width: 16px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 2.5px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .5);
    margin-left: 4px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .sbar-ic b::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 1.5px;
    right: 35%;
    border-radius: 1px;
    background: rgba(243, 227, 194, .9);
  }

  /* ============ screen · Entra (auth) ============ */
  .abody {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 11px;
    padding: 0 22px 26px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .atitle {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: "Clash Display", system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  .asub {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .58);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .afield {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 13px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .06);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .28);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .acaret {
    width: 1.5px;
    height: 15px;
    margin-left: 2px;
    background: #fff;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .acaret {
      animation: blink 1.05s steps(1, end) infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 49% { opacity: 1; }
      50%, 100% { opacity: 0; }
    }
  }

  .abtn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 13px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f7eedd, #e9d6b0);
    color: #231a10;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 22px -8px rgba(232, 207, 160, .35);
  }

  .adiv {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 4px 0;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .4);
  }

  .adiv::before,
  .adiv::after {
    content: "";
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .14);
  }

  .asso {
    display: flex;
    gap: 7px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .sso {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 10px 4px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .16);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .85);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .sso .mk {
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .sso .mk.wa {
    color: #3ddc84;
  }

  .sso .mk.fb {
    color: #5cc6ff;
  }

  .aperks {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .aperks span {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .62);
  }

  .aperks span::before {
    content: "✓";
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--lux);
  }

  /* ============ screen · Crea (event editor) ============ */
  .chead {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 9px 16px 7px;
  }

  .chead b {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    font-family: "Clash Display", system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  .cx {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .4);
  }

  .bce {
    font-size: 44px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, .35));
  }

  /* event gradient thumbs (hero palette colors) */
  .gx-fire { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2643c, #9c2310); }
  .gx-cake { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d95b92, #dfae52); }
  .gx-grad { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b3873f, #e3c684); }
  .gx-trip { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3aa697, #4f9fcb); }
  .gx-fest { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6b3bd1, #c2418a); }

  .covprev {
    margin: 0 16px;
    height: 132px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 52px rgba(0, 0, 0, .28);
  }

  .covprev .bce {
    font-size: 38px;
  }

  .covphoto {
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .covphoto::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: inherit;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, .55), transparent 55%);
  }

  .covtag {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
    bottom: 8px;
    left: 9px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .5);
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .14em;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .covpick {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 9px 16px 2px;
  }

  .sw {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    opacity: .7;
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sw.on {
    opacity: 1;
    outline: 2px solid var(--lux);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .sw.on::after {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, .6);
  }

  .swlbl {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .45);
    margin-left: 2px;
  }

  .cfield {
    margin: 8px 16px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .06);
    border: 1px solid var(--hair);
  }

  .cfield small {
    font-size: 8.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .42);
  }

  .cfield b {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .cfield.focus {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .4);
  }

  .cgrid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
    margin: 8px 16px 0;
  }

  .cgrid .cfield {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cbtn {
    margin: auto 16px 16px;
    padding: 13px;
    border-radius: 13px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f7eedd, #e9d6b0);
    color: #231a10;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 22px -8px rgba(232, 207, 160, .35);
  }

  /* ============ screen · Comparte (share) ============ */
  .shero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3px;
    padding: 14px 16px 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .shero .big {
    font-size: 34px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .shero b {
